            "descriptionRaw": "Xiao dons the Yaksha Mask that set gods and demons trembling millennia ago.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Yaksha's Mask</color>\n·Greatly increases Xiao's jumping ability.\n·Increases his attack AoE and attack DMG.\n·Converts attack DMG into <color=#80FFD7FF>Anemo DMG</color>, which cannot be overridden by any other elemental infusion.\n\nIn this state, Xiao will continuously lose HP.\nThe effects of this skill end when Xiao leaves the field.\n\n<i>Donning the Mask of the Yaksha, Xiao takes the terrifying, demon-conquering form of the Vigilant Yaksha. But this great power has also brought him great suffering. Some call him \"The Bane of All Evil.\"</i>",
            "name": "Bane of All Evil"
        },
